        Excelling in middle and high school and applying to college is no easy task. In fact, it can be quite stressful on teens. In today’s competitive admissions landscape the question remains: How can students stand out   in a crowded applicant pool and gain admission to increasingly selective colleges and universities? Although many college counselors demand expensive annual contracts, academic stratEDGEy offers targeted group seminars to keep you informed, organized, and on track. Through this innovative approach, Bree equips students and parents with the information and tools they need to successfully navigate the college admissions process.

